item.title: Welcome
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Our quality of life depends on the quality of our leaders. And since no one else seems to be volunteering, it’s up to you. If you’ve ever had dreams of leadership, NOW is the time, THIS is the place, and YOU’RE IT! Warren Bennis offered this invitation years ago. You are being called to answer it right now. Now is the time for you and for us to be in serious communication about the issues are most compelling. To be leaders today, we must be leaders for a future that is relentlessly emerging, seemingly without reference to what once worked. This is as evident in the institutional failures and floundering within our first-world cultures, as in the nascent forms emerging from the third-world. What we can experience is that hierarchy is in decline and decay, which means that self-responsibility must rise. This changes the role of the leaders from today forward to become builders of this self-responsibility among all stake holders. Leaders must provide access to information, if those led are going to think for themselves and have more say-so in their own lives. Leaders must become coaches, engendering more awareness and more responsibility in all they impact, as we move from the era of growth based on imposed rules into this emerging era of sustainability based on inner values. We welcome you in joining us in service to this inevitable transition from
  • Quantity to Quality
  • Excess to Stability
  • Teaching to Learning
  • Independence to Interdependence
  • Success to Service
  • Controlling Nature to Natural Controls
  • Hierarchy to Responsibility
Now IS the time, this IS the place, and together we ARE the leaders for this time.
